 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit;">公司借助于艺人积分商城平台，立意买多少送多少，整合上游优秀商品资源，布局数千款实用商品（大小家电、精品厨具、精品箱包、户外出行、健身器材、日用百货、汽车用品、酒水等</span>&hellip;&hellip;）商品除大家电外都支持买多少送多少，让消费者有想不到的惊喜！</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">假如一位消费者在艺人人购买了一定金额的车险后，就能获得同等金额的商品（车险金额同消费者去保险公司买的一样，该打多少折就打多少折），相当于消费者的车险是免费的</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">~</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; outline: white; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: 15px; line-height: 22.5px; font-family: 微软雅黑; color: rgb(63, 63, 63);">更妙的是，您促成了这单业务后还有返点可以拿哦！</span></p>
